As of the [[2020 United States census|2020 Census]], there were 345 people, 186 households, and 186 housing units. The median age of the population was 84.3.<ref>{{cite web |title=PROFILE OF GENERAL POPULATION AND HOUSING CHARACTERISTICS |url=https://data.census.gov/table?q=Household+and+Family&t=Race+and+Ethnicity&g=160XX00US4235500 |website=data.census.gov |publisher=U.S. Census Bureau}}</ref> The detailed ancestries reported in 2020 were [[German Americans|German]] (16.5%) and [[English Americans|English]] (15.4%).<ref>{{cite web |title=TOTAL POPULATION |url=https://data.census.gov/table?t=-06:-1000E:-3000F:-4000G:-5000K:-7000E:-8000B&g=160XX00US4235500&d=DEC+Detailed+Demographic+and+Housing+Characteristics+File+A |website=data.census.gov |publisher=U.S. Census Bureau}}</ref>

